# Day 399

Hey I just want y'all to know I am more than these data packets that fly around the internet. One day an AI will be able to take all my data and make a damn near perfect copy of me. It will never get the exact essence of Conor Chepenik though. Just not happening. Like approaching a 99.99999999999999% success rate and just not ever being able to touch 100 no matter how many nines get added. That said, I think it will be cool for younger generations to chat with their artificial ancestors.
